  "detailed_description": "<h1>JION OUR DISCORD</h1><p><br>DISCORD:</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UFO is a short stream-of-consciousness visual novel.</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/c292463f448a3f5c94a26c075a6efc02.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UFO</strong> is a boy's summer dream, a fragmented, brief, and surrealistic visual experience.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/833014e367521c27b98dfe460e51500e.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Teenager Plan, who is in middle school, is filled with confusion about the unknown. Like all children of this age, he is intrigued by the new and mysterious aspects of the world and humanity, while also harboring fear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.poster.avif?t=1761319405\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.webm?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134540/extras/dd17a4026d0c04e5bb9fac2158c6371e.mp4?t=1761319405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In his dream, he encounters her, them, and it. The player takes on the role of Plan and experiences this summer dream together.",
